Last Broadcast Date: Thu 1 Sep 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the Afghan woman who ran secret schools for girls under the Taliban - and still faces death threats in her fight to improve women's rights in her country. And, the priest in the Philippines who has come up with a novel way of campaigning for causes he believes in - he goes running. Show less